      <title>Xcel Energy 将在强风期间切断科罗拉多州部分地区的电力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/xcel-energy-to-cut-power-in-parts-of-colorado-amid-high-winds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Xcel Energy表示，由于大风可能会导致电线倒塌并引发野火，该公司将切断科罗拉多州约55,000名客户的电力。]]></description>
